{
  "stem": "26609.17",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And some sick people on the way, I had to deliver to check-- we stopped at each country to deliver the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was only one American captain who never was with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was in somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He had all the documents, who he's-- he's caring what people, where they go, from where they came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was a chaos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he-- so-- we-- I delivered to Czechoslovakia, I remember Prague, in a hospital, about 20 sick people-- very ill people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't know if they lived or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then I had some in-- no, from Czechoslovakia, I came-- I think Transylvania on the way to Poland, up there from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then we came to Poland [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I never could-- never dreamt of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was in the Russian hands to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And from [NON-ENGLISH] to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And when I was free, I could stay two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I had documents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I could stay and go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I went about three times like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Only I didn't-- no one forced me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But I wanted to find out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Meanwhile that I stayed there for two weeks, I could stay, to find out about my child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no that's a long story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a story for itself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I want to tell you, in Krakow when I was, I went to the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, I told them what happened, that I finished with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had to go back to-- and again back for transport people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't pay me for it, only with food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There, I went to the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't go anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had to go more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I tell you what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a long story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
